message.content: Restructured the story page with a captivating hero section and organized content sections. Added founder and production kitchen photos to "Our Sweet Journey," incorporated team imagery for "Meet the Dough Dream Team," and transformed philosophy sections into three elegant side-by-side cards. New sections for "Our Team" and "Testimonials" enhance the narrative, while the heartfelt closing message creates an inviting conclusion that encourages community and sharing.

Created a comprehensive menu page with an elegant layout showcasing DoughHeaven's delicious offerings. The page features categorized sections for signature donuts, seasonal specials, and beverages with appealing product cards that include images, descriptions, and prices. Added interactive filtering options and maintained consistent branding with the story page for a cohesive user experience.
